rows.label: qev013802_MSG0001
rows.name:
I work in arms development here in New LA,
you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013802_MSG0002
rows.name:
It's rewarding work, but I find navigating Earth customs
so so difficult...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013802_MSG0003
rows.name:
Evening comes and the entire team goes home, right?
But but to me, the dark hours are my most productive.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013802_SEL0011
rows.name: Suggest that Arwae take part in Alex's seminar.

rows.label: qev013802_MSG0004
rows.name:
His name is Alex, yes? Alex? Ah. Perhaps his seminar
will give me new insights into human thinking, maybe?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013802_MSG0005
rows.name:
I'll go, yes? Though perhaps I shouldn't expect too too
much, should I? Not to be rude...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013802_MSG0006
rows.name:
Perhaps. But but I'm afraid there is no time to waste,
right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013802_MSG0007
rows.name:
It would be so so helpful if you humans could teach
your customs to us Ma-non, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013802_MSG0008
rows.name:
So I might not be the only one experiencing difficulty,
right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013802_MSG0009
rows.name: I'll look forward to maybe attending Alex's seminar.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013802_MSG0010
rows.name:
I will spare no effort in learning how to function well
with humans, okay? Okay![ST:wait ]
